description._content: Thank you for all the fun on Flickr this year! You have helped us to date/locate many photos in our collection and your stories help to bring many of these to life. We hope to see you will all again next year. Best wishes, Anthea, Anna, Rhonda, Fiona and Jenny PS We started a Flickr Group called Archives2Share NSW. If you have ever visited our reading rooms to view original archives - and took photos of them - then we'd love you to join us on the group. Images posted there will become available in our experimental catalogue search tool. You'll be helping us to make the NSW state archives more accessible.
